{"tid":2351381,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實曹操個寧我負天下人，莫要天下人負我個故仔係咪咁","createTime":"2021-01-03T07:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T07:33:53.000Z","uid":282619,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a261b50aafd34c9e51361b79dc77d6430aca2cd","tid":2351381,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T07:13:57.000Z","msg":"佢就刺殺董卓衰咗，就着草，借宿朋友屋企<br />\n同曹操同行條友就問佢，佢會唔會背叛我哋<br />\n曹操就話唔會嘅，佢係我老死<br />\n結果曹操半夜聽到磨刀聲，個心怯一怯，以為佢老死想做尻佢<br />\n就把心一橫，我做尻你先好過你做尻我先<br />\n結果就做尻佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但其實佢老死想磨刀切豬肉比佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再話寧我負天下人，莫要天下人負我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後同佢同行條友見佢咁都買佢怕，走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽落真係幾搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdb63cd1874e5c74d072004362f8f2341146f51","tid":2351381,"uid":224561,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T07:18:23.000Z","msg":"個朋友好似係陳官"},{"pid":"0f301fd6fe4310065d9d1426e092833a9e19c8ef","tid":2351381,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T07:18:52.000Z","msg":"柒左要攞返個彩姐，唔使認真"},{"pid":"6be22dd16f20f7404c9f5be4939d7307b9af6f53","tid":2351381,"uid":282619,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f301fd6fe4310065d9d1426e092833a9e19c8ef","tid":2351381,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T07:18:52.000Z","msg":"柒左要攞返個彩姐，唔使認真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢點知人哋要殺豬，唔係殺佢<br />\n殺錯人<img src=\"/asset